.Dd July 13, 2003
.Dt ZZZ 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm zzz
.Nd suspend an ACPI or APM system
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility
checks for
.Tn ACPI
or
.Tn APM
support and then suspends the system appropriately.
For
.Tn APM ,
.Pp
.Dl apm -z
.Pp
will be issued.
For
.Tn ACPI,
the configured suspend state will be looked up, checked to see
if it is supported and,
.Pp
.Dl acpiconf -s <state>
.Pp
will be issued.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr acpi 4 ,
.Xr apm 4 ,
.Xr acpiconf 8 ,
.Xr apm 8
